title: Biden Pitches Economy in New Mexico
description: President Biden’s stop in New Mexico was heavy on statistics, as he sought to persuade Americans that the economy is doing better on his watch.
dc:creator: The Associated Press

media:content.media:credit: Tom Brenner for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: President Biden’s stop in New Mexico opened a five-day swing that will also take him to California, Illinois, Pennsylvania, Delaware, New York and Maryland by Election Day.
